<sect2>
<title>Introduction to <application>daemontools</application></title>

<para>The <application>daemontools</application> package is a replacement for 
<application>inetd</application> or <application>xinetd</application>. The main 
reason for using it here is because it is recommended for use with 
<application>qmail</application> and <application>djbdns</application>.</para>

